QuestData.Title: The King's Command
QuestData.Description: Greetings, $c.$B$BI have been asked to assemble a team for a high priority mission.$B$BPlease come to Stormwind Keep immediately for a briefing with King Varian Wrynn. I will be waiting in the King's war room.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: This is a matter of utmost urgency...and secrecy.
QuestData.LogDescription: Find Grand Admiral Jes-Tereth in the war room at Stormwind Keep in Stormwind City.
QuestData.RewardText: Our role is of utmost importance. Admiral Taylor and his flagship have gone missing. More importantly, the young Prince was with him, and it is our primary objective to bring him back home safely.
